The paper deals with the design of pilot sequences for multi-cell massive MIMO networks, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also considers the impact of large-scale propagation effects on the user load, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper deals with the optimization of the pilot sequences, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and communication (cs.COM) systems.
